        {
            "title": "霍爾木茲海峽航運似乎依然凍結 儘管伊朗嘗試收取「過路費」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 伊朗戰爭爆發四周以來，關鍵石油通道霍爾木茲海峽的船舶通行似乎仍基本停滯，儘管德黑蘭試圖建立通行費機制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">基於船舶自動識別系統(AIS)信號的追蹤數據顯示，周四僅有4艘散貨船和2艘液化石油氣運輸船通過該水道，過去7天合計為39艘。相比之下，2025年平均每天有近60艘商船通行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩艘與中國國有企業中國遠洋海運集團有關聯的大型貨櫃船曾試圖通過霍爾木茲海峽駛離波斯灣，但在接近伊朗時突然掉頭返回。據半官方的邁赫爾通訊社報導，伊朗周五迫使三艘不同國籍的貨櫃船掉頭返回。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3a68158f-bf65-3297-adac-f9b679b08678-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/27EVmrYEAZJMzOxB47CPbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5bc84ae58c87f368597e2dee8a7c4556\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管伊朗嘗試建立收費體系、單個航次「過路費」最高可達200萬美元，但這一舉措似乎並未提振通行量。德黑蘭本周還表示，將禁止「敵對」國家船隻通過，這意味著部分其他國家船隻可能被允許通行。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">追蹤數據還顯示，川普聲稱伊朗允許10艘油輪通行的「禮物」目前似乎尚未兌現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">需要指出的是，部分船隻可能悄悄通行，使得實際通行情況難以精確判斷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多數船隻在通過該水道時會關閉信號設備，只有在遠離後才重新開啟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，該地區的衛星圖像存在延遲，也進一步增加了觀測難度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五，伊朗和以色列繼續互相發射飛彈，德黑蘭還將目標對准了海灣國家。沙烏地阿拉伯報告稱已攔截飛往利雅得的無人機和飛彈，多哈響起警報，科威特港口則在無人機襲擊中受損。以色列方面稱，正加大對伊朗軍事基礎設施的打擊力度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：少許船隻沿伊朗海岸穿越霍爾木茲海峽 另闢蹊徑的航跡指向伊朗放行</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五有消息稱，希臘船東Dynacom Tankers Management Ltd.派出至少第三艘油輪通過該海峽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為了捕捉關閉應答器的船隻，彭博既追蹤在遠離霍爾木茲後重新出現的船隻，也追蹤從波斯灣消失的船隻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hormuz Ship Traffic Stays Frozen Despite Move to Start Charging</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(第三段更新兩艘中國貨櫃船掉頭折返的信息)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
