        },
        {
            "title": "日圓兌美元2024年以來首次跌破160關口 東京當局干預風險上升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 由於中東局勢持續緊張，日圓跌破1美元兌160日圓這一關鍵水平，加劇了東京當局干預風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五，日圓兌美元跌幅高達0.3%，觸及160.21，為2024年7月以來的最低水平，距離161.95僅咫尺之遙，若達到該水平將創下1986年以來的最低紀錄。交易員一直關注160關口，因為日本當局上次出手支持日圓就在這一水平附近。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場壓力反映了能源價格飆升對日本構成的經濟威脅，這正在推高通膨，傷害消費者和企業。日圓貶值提高了日本干預匯市的可能性，財務大臣周五早些時候暗示或採取「果斷行動」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b219b2a5-2a7c-38ad-8048-8319972790a0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三菱日聯摩根士丹利證券首席債券策略師Naomi Muguruma表示：「財年結束之際交易清淡，債市可能因周末川普立場的變化而出現震盪。最令人擔憂的是停火談判可能破裂，衝突或將升級，從而限制全球能源流動，導致最壞情況下的滯脹局面。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xI0JBWuJCzT7z.oJ2SUGqg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/641c4972ebe3c092d7dac76a41ade561\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Yen Weakens to 160 Against Dollar for First Time Since 2024</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Masahiro Hidaka、Alice French、Takahiko Hyuga.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
